    <title>Set Up DNN</title>

    <body>

        <section id="DNNProducts">
            <p>DNN offers three products:
                <ul>
                    <li>DNN Platform is the free open-source package.</li>
                    <li>Evoq Content adds more advanced website management features over the DNN Platform.</li>
                    <li>Evoq Engage adds user engagement features over Evoq Content.</li>
                </ul>
            </p>

            <p>You can <xref format="html" scope="external" href="http://www.dnnsoftware.com/products/compare-dnn-platform-to-evoq">compare the features</xref> in detail.</p>

            <p>Then, <xref format="dita" href="../../common/placeholderlink.dita">download DNN here</xref>.</p>

