        <section id="DNNRequirements">
            <p>For a basic installation, DNN requires Microsoft IIS and SQL server. You can view the <xref format="dita" href="../Requirements.dita">DNN 8.0 Requirements</xref> for the compatible versions.</p>
            <p><b>Developers:</b> Visual Studio 2015 is the recommended IDE for developing DNN modules. It is required if you are contributing to the DNN Platform.</p>
